      "comment": "DELICATE RULER (3) scored at his most recent appearance, getting home by 1.75 lengths over 1100m at this track. That continued the good form this campaign, with two wins from four runs. Take catching again. BEYOND THE WALL (5) was a winner here two back then had no luck off a wide draw last time. Gets a chance to atone. OUTLAW MUSIC (7) went fast early over 1120m at Derby last time and defied all challengers to score by 3 lengths. This is harder but drops in weight and can give a sight again. OCEAN OUTLAW (8) is capable of featuring on his best form. FIRE THE GUARD (4) has placed 4/4 when fresh and is expected to run well.",
